---
title: Bison Meatballs with Pear-Apricot Chutney
description: Sauces are the star of tonight's dinner! The pear-apricot chutney brings tart sweetness to rich bison meatballs, while spinach dressed in a bacon-maple-Dijon vinaigrette adds another layer of classic Canadian flavours to this tasty dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-bison-d5c02425.jpg
